00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:05,952 --> 00:01:08,384
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,512 --> 00:01:11,424
=Episode 20=

3
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:12,799
One.

4
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:14,180
Two.

5
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:15,500
Three.

6
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:16,540
Four.

7
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:17,500
Five.

8
00:01:17,959 --> 00:01:18,459
Six.

9
00:01:18,959 --> 00:01:19,480
Seven.

10
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:20,700
Eight.

11
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,840
It's so hard to survive the harem.

12
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:27,200
The Empress Dowager pressures us
to have an heir.

13
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:30,359
The Empress forces us to exercise.

14
00:01:30,879 --> 00:01:33,400
But I haven't
even touched His Majesty's hand.

15
00:01:34,959 --> 00:01:38,480
Back when His Majesty favored me,

16
00:01:38,480 --> 00:01:40,359
he summoned me very often.

17
00:01:40,480 --> 00:01:43,519
His Majesty did touch my hand.

18
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:47,159
I'm so envious.

19
00:01:47,159 --> 00:01:48,079
I want that too.

20
00:01:48,079 --> 00:01:49,799
But you and His Majesty

21
00:01:50,599 --> 00:01:51,959
slept in separate beds.

22
00:01:52,079 --> 00:01:53,920
What nonsense!

23
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,799
I thought I was unlucky,

24
00:01:56,959 --> 00:01:59,599
assuming His Majesty just preferred you.

25
00:02:00,159 --> 00:02:03,560
So you also noticed
that His Majesty has feelings for me?

26
00:02:07,099 --> 00:02:08,800
Then... why?

27
00:02:08,879 --> 00:02:12,000
Could it be
because His Majesty is impotent?

28
00:02:13,879 --> 00:02:15,479
His Majesty has never slept in my place.

29
00:02:17,340 --> 00:02:17,840
Yeah.

30
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:20,640
Shut up! Do you want to die?

31
00:02:21,408 --> 00:02:24,680
His Majesty is healthy. Very healthy.

32
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,439
What's going on?

33
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,319
- Your Majesty.
- Your Majesty.

34
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:34,319
Your Majesty.

35
00:02:34,479 --> 00:02:37,319
I was praising
how strong His Majesty is.

36
00:02:39,879 --> 00:02:40,759
Your Majesty.

37
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:43,120
See how well we've been training.

38
00:02:44,919 --> 00:02:48,919
Then, you shall hold your horse stance
for an extra hour today.

39
00:02:52,159 --> 00:02:52,719
Yes.

40
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:04,520
(Although I wish
Xiao Jinyun would only be with me,)

41
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:06,759
(Zhao Qiluo
and the others are innocent.)

42
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,759
(Should they be forced
into lifelong loneliness?)

43
00:03:17,439 --> 00:03:18,439
I knew I'd find you here.

44
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:29,639
I can relax a bit

45
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:31,400
only when I'm with you.

46
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:35,360
You must have heard
about the situation outside.

47
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:40,680
It's sort of a state affair,
causing quite the stir.

48
00:03:41,319 --> 00:03:42,159
I've heard about it.

49
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:46,240
They all have their eyes fixed
on my harem,

50
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:49,080
eager to have my heir come
from their own clan,

51
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:52,000
so they can partake in the royal power.

52
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:55,319
So, who in this court can I trust?

53
00:03:57,520 --> 00:04:00,199
Your Majesty,
I can fight on the battlefield.

54
00:04:00,599 --> 00:04:02,400
I also won't fear facing your subjects.

55
00:04:02,879 --> 00:04:04,080
No matter what happens,

56
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:07,960
I will stand by your side.

57
00:04:18,879 --> 00:04:19,680
Xu Yu.

58
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:24,720
They are pressuring me to depose you
and expand the harem.

59
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:29,160
As the Empress,
are you truly not jealous?

60
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:34,480
Who says I'm not?

61
00:04:35,319 --> 00:04:36,240
It's just that...

62
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,959
They are right on some points.

63
00:04:42,079 --> 00:04:44,480
So you mean I should
restart the concubine selection?

64
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:46,480
Xiao Jinyun.

65
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:49,720
We have no doubts about each other
and can face it together.

66
00:04:50,279 --> 00:04:51,839
But I think

67
00:04:52,439 --> 00:04:55,160
Consort Zhao and the others
haven't done anything wrong.

68
00:04:55,519 --> 00:04:58,120
Must they be trapped
and wither away in the palace?

69
00:04:58,879 --> 00:05:02,368
I wish to request that once Your Majesty
roots out the treacherous officials,

70
00:05:03,020 --> 00:05:06,240
could you please
seriously consider their future?

71
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:12,600
No worries,
I have a plan for this matter.

72
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:15,519
Anyway,

73
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:19,600
I have something more important
to do with you right now.

74
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,480
What is it?

75
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:26,079
Xu Yu, how about you bear me a child?

76
00:05:27,399 --> 00:05:28,800
What are you talking about?

77
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,920
Xu Ziping,
based on the Three-Pillar Method,

78
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:57,519
invented the Four-Pillar Method.

79
00:05:58,439 --> 00:05:59,560
Interesting.

80
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:02,480
Your Highness, you...

81
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:06,959
Since Queen of Dada has left,

82
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:09,800
Jinyun should be able to sleep soundly.

83
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:11,920
As for me, I can finally get some rest,

84
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,959
no more being a spy and tracking her.

85
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:14,920
Your Highness.

86
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:17,319
If you are tired,

87
00:06:17,839 --> 00:06:19,959
you can return to your place
and rest properly.

88
00:06:19,959 --> 00:06:23,240
You're mistaken.
I'm in high spirits right now,

89
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:26,160
free from official duties.
I feel so good.

90
00:06:29,879 --> 00:06:31,000
Have you heard?

91
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:34,560
His Majesty argued
with the subjects in court again.

92
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:37,079
He said there will be
no more concubine selections.

93
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:39,040
He will only have the Empress's child.

94
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:41,199
Then what about us?

95
00:06:41,639 --> 00:06:43,920
Xu Yu is such a vixen.

96
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:46,639
Does she want
to have His Majesty to herself?

97
00:06:46,959 --> 00:06:48,319
Exactly.

98
00:06:49,399 --> 00:06:53,199
Now the Empress Dowager pressures us
to bear children. But how?

99
00:06:53,199 --> 00:06:57,079
Actually, as long as they don't
lower our ranks or allowances,

100
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:59,360
I find the life here agreeable.

101
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:00,920
That's what you think.

102
00:07:02,959 --> 00:07:04,839
His Majesty...

103
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:07,560
His Majesty once held me.

104
00:07:08,839 --> 00:07:09,639
He held her.

105
00:07:09,639 --> 00:07:13,120
I don't believe Xu Yu has His Majesty
to herself forever?

106
00:07:13,519 --> 00:07:15,480
Everyone arrived quite early today.

107
00:07:18,199 --> 00:07:19,680
- Greetings, Your Majesty.
- Greetings, Your Majesty.

108
00:07:19,959 --> 00:07:20,720
Rise.

109
00:07:21,399 --> 00:07:22,439
Your Majesty.

110
00:07:22,839 --> 00:07:26,319
We've been practicing the moves
you taught us.

111
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,240
We've improved a lot.

112
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,480
Well done.

113
00:07:29,839 --> 00:07:31,879
Today, we'll learn a new move.

114
00:07:32,279 --> 00:07:34,600
Consort Zhao,
let's demonstrate it for everyone.

115
00:07:34,879 --> 00:07:36,500
Shall we show everyone an example?

116
00:07:38,199 --> 00:07:38,699
Okay.

117
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,540
Turn right, dodge.

118
00:07:42,759 --> 00:07:43,360
Well done.

119
00:07:46,160 --> 00:07:46,759
Your turn.

120
00:07:51,839 --> 00:07:52,339
Good.

121
00:07:56,300 --> 00:07:57,399
- Your Majesty.
- It wasn't me.

122
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:58,839
- I didn't even touch her!
- Your Majesty.

123
00:07:58,839 --> 00:07:59,600
Your Majesty.

124
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,560
Jiang Tang, what's wrong?

125
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,720
Your Majesty, congrats!

126
00:08:12,279 --> 00:08:14,199
Her Majesty is pregnant.

127
00:08:15,959 --> 00:08:16,680
What?

128
00:08:19,279 --> 00:08:19,800
Really?

129
00:08:20,279 --> 00:08:21,040
Physician Jiang.

130
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:24,759
Is she truly pregnant?

131
00:08:24,959 --> 00:08:26,720
I'm very sure.

132
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:29,120
This time, she truly is pregnant.

133
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:33,639
Heaven blesses us!
I will soon have a grandchild.

134
00:08:34,759 --> 00:08:36,200
I'm already pregnant?

135
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:39,039
Someone, assist me to the prayer hall!

136
00:08:39,279 --> 00:08:42,120
I must pray for Xu Yu
and the child she is carrying.

137
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:44,039
Mother,

138
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,919
the Directorate of Astronomy
will do that.

139
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:48,799
My grandchild deserves my personal care.

140
00:08:49,159 --> 00:08:51,679
You stay with Xu Yu
and do not upset her.

141
00:08:52,039 --> 00:08:52,919
Yes, Mother.

142
00:08:53,519 --> 00:08:55,480
Xu Yu, rest well.

143
00:08:56,500 --> 00:08:57,000
Yes.

144
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:57,639
Mother.

145
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,480
Let me help you.

146
00:09:19,759 --> 00:09:21,600
Stop staring at me.

147
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:24,960
What are you doing?

148
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,600
I want some water.

149
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:27,100
I'll get it.

150
00:09:27,159 --> 00:09:27,659
No need.

151
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,320
I'm not that fragile.

152
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:32,360
This isn't about fragility.

153
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,879
You're pregnant now.

154
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,600
Take care not only of yourself

155
00:09:36,919 --> 00:09:38,559
but also of our child.

156
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:42,320
Xu Yu, thank you.

157
00:09:43,879 --> 00:09:46,080
For giving me another family
in this world.

158
00:09:46,559 --> 00:09:49,720
From now on, I will protect you both.

159
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,679
We've bought the supplements,

160
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:03,039
but without the jade
for the expectant Empress.

161
00:10:03,519 --> 00:10:05,279
But with so many jade shops
on this street,

162
00:10:06,039 --> 00:10:07,440
which one should we choose?

163
00:10:15,799 --> 00:10:18,200
Your Highness,
Her Majesty's element is metal.

164
00:10:19,159 --> 00:10:20,759
Today, the southeast is most auspicious.

165
00:10:21,039 --> 00:10:23,039
Coral and tourmaline
are her lucky stones.

166
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:25,600
But there are no gold shops
to the southeast.

167
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:28,080
I also want to buy a longevity lock
for my future nephew.

168
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:30,879
May he live a long, healthy life.

169
00:10:31,679 --> 00:10:32,320
Your Highness.

170
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:35,759
Longevity locks are usually gifts
from elders.

171
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,960
So what? I am an elder.

172
00:10:38,639 --> 00:10:40,480
He will be my closest nephew.

173
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,879
He deserves the best.

174
00:10:43,759 --> 00:10:45,039
Your Highness likes children?

175
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:46,159
Of course!

176
00:10:46,879 --> 00:10:48,840
They're small, soft,

177
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:51,240
and smell nice. So adorable!

178
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:55,279
Today, you all came specifically
to congratulate me on my pregnancy

179
00:10:55,759 --> 00:10:58,720
with precious gifts. I am deeply moved.

180
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:02,720
I hope you all can enjoy yourselves.

181
00:11:04,799 --> 00:11:05,879
- Thanks, Your Majesty.
- Thanks, Your Majesty.

182
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:12,860
Take it.

183
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:16,860
It's yours.

184
00:11:31,759 --> 00:11:32,919
Greetings, Your Majesty.

185
00:11:33,399 --> 00:11:36,240
My mother is unwell and unable to come.

186
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:37,679
She sent me in her stead.

187
00:11:39,879 --> 00:11:42,320
This is a top-grade red coral bracelet.

188
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:46,519
May it bring you peace and joy
wherever you are.

189
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:48,559
Thank you so much.

190
00:12:16,399 --> 00:12:17,320
Your Majesty!

191
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:39,120
Xu Yu!

192
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,120
Virtuous Consort.

193
00:12:54,120 --> 00:12:54,720
Xu Yu!

194
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:57,679
Your Majesty.

195
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,600
Summon Jiang Tang!

196
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:03,720
Are you alright?

197
00:13:04,039 --> 00:13:06,399
I'm fine. Virtuous Consort is injured.

198
00:13:06,799 --> 00:13:07,879
And Xiao Jinle.

199
00:13:08,799 --> 00:13:11,519
Thanks to him,
Virtuous Consort and I were saved.

200
00:13:13,559 --> 00:13:14,960
It was an honor

201
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:17,440
to protect Your Majesty.

202
00:13:20,279 --> 00:13:23,919
Miss Sun, Count Cheng'en's daughter?
Why did you attempt to assassinate me?

203
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,200
A poison in her mouth.

204
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:30,919
She killed herself.

205
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:37,879
Your Highness.

206
00:13:39,639 --> 00:13:40,416
Virtuous Consort.

207
00:14:07,642 --> 00:14:12,826
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

208
00:14:13,562 --> 00:14:18,125
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

209
00:14:19,450 --> 00:14:24,865
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

210
00:14:25,434 --> 00:14:29,978
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

211
00:14:30,618 --> 00:14:35,882
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

212
00:14:36,250 --> 00:14:41,927
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

213
00:14:42,266 --> 00:14:44,282
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

214
00:14:44,474 --> 00:14:48,218
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

215
00:14:48,794 --> 00:14:53,466
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

216
00:14:54,010 --> 00:14:55,770
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

217
00:14:56,090 --> 00:14:59,706
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

218
00:14:59,953 --> 00:15:05,480
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪

